  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.interfaces.EmbeddingComponentStateAccessI

    public class Heating
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.AbstractCyPhyComponent
implements fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.interfaces.EmbeddingComponentStateAccessI
    This class represents the heating of the house, it can be turned on/off, it has a modular power (and so a modular consumption), and inform the temperature sensor of the produced heat
    Author:
    Julien Xavier et Alexis Belanger
